Subject: Re: [T2] solar trickle chargers

Have one, love it. Kept a pair of group 27 gel batteries alive for eleven
years on my boat before I sold the boat. Now lives on the dash of my van.
The small ones like this don't put out enough power to require any kind of
regulation, so are safe to keep on all the time.

